<SYNC START=2750000><P Class=EGCC>
The only one Mother could be proud of.
<SYNC START=2751600><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=2752800><P Class=EGCC>
Money was important to Mother.
<SYNC START=2754300><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=2756500><P Class=EGCC>
She bought me for 100 pounds, Doctor. <br>
