from that desk.
<SYNC START=2865700><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=2867100><P Class=EGCC>
Have you asked yourself how he got it?
<SYNC START=2869300><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=2869800><P Class=EGCC>
Inspector. Miss Marple.
<SYNC START=2871300><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=2871500><P Class=EGCC>
Is there any chance <br>
