Yes. But I can't find anything.
<SYNC START=2986400><P Class=EGCC>
Surely something like that's more likely
<SYNC START=2988000><P Class=EGCC>
to be found in her study, isn't it?
<SYNC START=2989900><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=2991500><P Class=EGCC>
Yes.
<SYNC START=2992300><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=2994100><P Class=EGCC>
Yes.
<SYNC START=2995300><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=2996800><P Class=EGCC>
Will you help me, Miss Marple?
