<SYNC START=3081100><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=3086100><P Class=EGCC>
It's been cleared out.
<SYNC START=3087500><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=3094500><P Class=EGCC>
JOHN CROKER PRIVATE DETECTIVE
