<SYNC START=3124400><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=3126200><P Class=EGCC>
Well, yes, I understand that, Mr Croker,
<SYNC START=3128700><P Class=EGCC>
but you see, it's possible you might be
<SYNC START=3130700><P Class=EGCC>
able to help us with investig...
<SYNC START=3131900><P Class=EGCC>
I must stop you there, young lady,
<SYNC START=3133100><P Class=EGCC>
