<SYNC START=3138500><P Class=EGCC>
- I thought you said it was confidentiality.        <br>
- Good day.
<SYNC START=3141300><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=3141900><P Class=EGCC>
Wait. Wait, wait. Listen, Mr...
<SYNC START=3143200><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=3143500><P Class=EGCC>
Mr erm... Erm...<br>
